'''''Sankofa'''''  ni filime yerekana ikinamico yakozwe [[Etiyopiya|na Etiyopiya yo mu]] 1993 iyobowe na Haile Gerima yibanze ku bucuruzi bw’abacakara bwa Atlantike<ref>Sankofa movie review & film summary (2021) | Roger Ebert <nowiki>https://www.rogerebert.com</nowiki> › reviews › sankofa-movie...</ref> . Iyi nkuru igaragaramo Oyafunmike Ogunlano, Kofi Ghanaba, Mutabaruka, Alexandra Duah, na Afemo Omilami . Ijambo Sankofa ryakomotse ku rurimi rwa Akan rwo [[Gana|muri Gana]] risobanura "gusubira inyuma, gushaka, no kubona ubwenge, imbaraga n'ibyiringiro", nk'uko byavuzwe na Dr. Anna Julia Cooper<ref>'Sankofa': the movie that teaches us to go back to the past <nowiki>https://www.ft.com</nowiki> › content</ref>.  Ijambo Sankofa ryibanda ku kamaro ko umuntu atagendera kure cyane ya kahise kugirango atere imbere ejo hazaza<ref>SANKOFA | On Netflix September 24 - Array Now <nowiki>http://www.arraynow.com</nowiki> › sankofa</ref>. Muri filime, Sankofa agereranwa ninyoni n'indirimbo n'ingoma z'ingoma y'Imana<ref>Sankofa | UCLA Film & Television Archive <nowiki>https://www.cinema.ucla.edu</nowiki> › la-rebellion › films › san...</ref>.  Filime ya Gerima yerekanye akamaro ko kutagira abantu bakomoka muri [[Afurika]] batandukana n’imizi yabo. Gerima yakoresheje urugendo rwimico Mona kugirango yerekane uburyo imyumvire nyafurika yerekana indangamuntu harimo kumenya imizi yumuntu no "gusubira aho yaturutse" (Gerima)<ref>Sankofa: A Second Life for a Canonical African American Film <nowiki>https://www.original-cin.ca</nowiki> › posts › sankofa-a-second-l...</ref>.

== Umugambi ==
Filime itangirana numusaza Divine Drummer , Sankofa (yakinnye na Kofi Ghanaba ), akubita ingoma nyafurika aririmba imvugo ngo "Umwuka utinda w'abapfuye, haguruka<ref>Sankofa | UCLA Film & Television Archive <nowiki>https://www.cinema.ucla.edu</nowiki> › la-rebellion › films › san...</ref>." Ubu ni uburyo bwe bwo gushyikirana nabakurambere b'igihugu cya [[Afurika|Afrika]],  cyane [[Gana]]<ref>MOVIE REVIEW : 'Sankofa' Delivers Powerful Indictment of ... <nowiki>https://www.latimes.com</nowiki> › archives › la-xpm-1995-05-...</ref>. Yizera ko kuvuza ingoma ari ngombwa mu kugarura umwuka w'abakurambere be biciwe muri diaspora nyafurika<ref>Sankofa, un film éthiopien sur la résistance noire | Africanews <nowiki>https://fr.africanews.com</nowiki> › 2021/09/17</ref> .  Inkuru ikomeza kugaragaza Mona (Oyafunmike Ogunlano), wabayeho [[Afurika]] na [[Amerika]] ntangarugero kuri film shoot muri [[Gana|Ghana]] <ref>Sankofa – trigon-film.org <nowiki>https://www.trigon-film.org</nowiki> › movies</ref>. Afite isomo ku Kigo cya Cape Coast, atazi ko cyakoreshejwe mu mateka mu bucuruzi bw’abacakara   kubera ko kuva kera atandukanijwe n’imizi [[Afurika|ye yo muri Afurika]]<ref>Beik on , 'Sankofa' | H-Ideas | H-Net <nowiki>https://networks.h-net.org</nowiki> › node › reviews › beik-sank...</ref>[[Afurika|.]] Mugihe Mona ari kumurongo wicyitegererezo, ahura numusaza wamayobera Sankofa wavuzaga ingoma mugutangira film<ref>Black Cinema Aesthetics and the Filmic Language of Sankofa <nowiki>https://www.jstor.org</nowiki> › stable › framework.55.2.0171</ref>. Sankofa akomeje kwibutsa Mona gusubira mu mateka ye kandi akaba umunyamahane cyane mu bijyanye no gukomeza ahantu h'abasekuruza bera<ref>sankofa virtual film – Ghana Commission for UNESCO <nowiki>https://unescoghana.org</nowiki> › sankofa-virtual-film-2</ref>, bityo agerageza kwirukana ba mukerarugendo b'abazungu mu kigo cy'abacakara.  Iyo Mona ingingo kujya A Kureba imbere castle ubwe,  Mona agerageza guhunga urugo rw'abacakara ahura na ba shebuja b'abaja bera agerageza gutekereza avuga ko akomoka muri [[Amerika]] kandi ko adakomoka muri [[Afurika]]<ref>Exploring "Sankofa" - Amplify Africa <nowiki>https://www.amplifyafrica.org</nowiki> › post › exploring-sankofa</ref> . Ba shebuja b'abacakara ntibitaye ku byo Mona yavuze maze bamusunika ku muriro, bamwambura imyenda, bamushyira icyuma gishyushye ku mugongo<ref>What Movies About Slavery Teach Us About Race Relations ... <nowiki>https://www.theatlantic.com</nowiki> › archive › 2014/01 › what...</ref>.

